snippet.title: Pocket Bomberman - GBC Longplay/Walkthrough #1 [720p]
snippet.description:
Gameboy Color: Pocket Bomberman

Rating: 4/5

Such a fun game, controls are super spicy and feels kind of like a megaman game. I also love the bomb jumps. Definitely check this one out!
